Params: {1: 'Assets/Product/Texture/Image/BgStory/BgStory730.jpg'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Chrome', 3: "Ah, my apologies, Commandant. I shouldn't have mentioned work while you're on leave.", 4: '1'}
{2: 'Chrome', 3: "I... didn't expect us to clear the maze so efficiently.", 4: '1'}
{2: 'Chrome', 3: "Even though we rarely fight together, I feel like you can always perfectly intuit what I'm thinking for some reason, Commandant,", 4: '1'}
{2: 'That\'s probably our "rapport."', 3: '9', 4: 'That\'s probably the "rapport" of Chiefs from F.O.S.', 5: '9'}
{2: 'Chrome', 3: '...Is that so?', 4: '1'}
{3: 'Chrome looks at you and slowly smiles.'}
{2: 'Chrome', 3: "What a perfect vacation. I think I'll never forget this.", 4: '1'}
{2: 'Chrome', 3: "There's... still some time left?", 4: '1'}
{2: 'Chrome', 3: "Is there something else you want to do, Commandant? I noticed that you've been staring at that for a while.", 4: '1'}
{2: 'It seems like the perfect place to sit down and chat.', 3: '15'}
{3: 'You can keep talking about the maze-inspired tactical training exercise you just came up with or the battles you recently fought.'}
{3: 'Whatever the topic is, you always have a good time chatting with Chrome.'}
{2: 'Chrome', 3: "...It appears that we've gained a whole new kind of training exercise.", 4: '1'}
{3: 'Chrome smiles, having noted down the last bit of your ideas.'}
{2: "You're always very serious about work, Chrome.", 3: '20'}
{2: 'Chrome', 3: "It's probably because I have a goal I want to pursue.", 4: '1'}
{2: 'Chrome', 3: "As long as I have a goal, I'll be motivated to seek out the path toward achieving it.", 4: '1'}
{3: 'Chrome looks at you earnestly, his eyes sparking with determination.'}
{2: 'Chrome', 3: 'Should we refine our ideas, then, Commandant?', 4: '1'}
{2: 'What ideas do you have?', 3: '25'}
{2: 'Chrome', 3: "I think we should explore the maze again. This time, I'll do the guiding...", 4: '1'}
